---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 text-neutral-900 leading-relaxed">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1E758D]">Privacy Policy — Dictionapp</h1>

  <p class="mb-6">
    <strong>Company:</strong> Studio Muxa Tech, S.L. 
    <span class="px-2">|</span>
    <strong>Last updated:</strong> November 28, 2025
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>Dictionapp</strong> (the “App”), operated by 
    <strong>Studio Muxa Tech, S.L.</strong>, collects, uses, shares and protects personal data. 
    By using the App you accept the practices described here.
  </p>

  <!-- 1 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">1. Information We Collect</h2>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1.1 Information You Provide</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    <strong>Email address:</strong> Collected when signing in via Google or Apple. 
    We do not store passwords.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1.2 Information Collected Automatically</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Usage metrics such as feature usage, session duration, performance logs, 
    and anonymized technical identifiers for improvement of the App.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1.3 Sensitive Data</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    We do not intentionally collect sensitive personal data.
  </p>

  <!-- 2 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-6">
    <li>To enable secure sign-in and account identification.</li>
    <li>To provide App functionality.</li>
    <li>To analyze usage for product improvements.</li>
    <li>To process payments and subscriptions via app stores.</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-6">We do not sell personal data.</p>

  <!-- 3 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-6">
    <li><strong>Firebase (Google LLC)</strong> — authentication, analytics and infrastructure.</li>
    <li><strong>Google Play Billing</strong> / <strong>Apple In-App Purchases</strong> — payment processing.</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- 4 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">4. Geographic Scope & Compliance</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    The App operates in Spain and the United States, with planned expansion to the EU and LATAM. 
    GDPR protections apply to users in the European Union.
  </p>

  <!-- 5 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">5. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-6">
    <li><strong>Contract performance</strong> — providing App functionality.</li>
    <li><strong>Consent</strong> — when required for specific processing.</li>
    <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> — analytics and App improvement.</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- 6 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">6. Data Retention</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    Data is retained while your account remains active. Upon deletion request, data is removed 
    according to our providers’ technical retention schedules.
  </p>

  <!-- 7 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">7. User Rights</h2>

  <p class="mb-4">Depending on your region, you may:</p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-6">
    <li>Access your data.</li>
    <li>Request corrections.</li>
    <li>Request deletion.</li>
    <li>Object to certain processing.</li>
    <li>Request data portability.</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-6">
    <strong>Account deletion:</strong> Email  
    <a href="mailto:dictionapp.muxatech@gmail.com" class="underline">
      dictionapp.muxatech@gmail.com
    </a>  
    with the subject “Delete Dictionapp account”.
  </p>

  <!-- 8 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">8. Security</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    We apply reasonable technical and organizational measures, including encryption 
    and secure infrastructure (Firebase). Absolute security cannot be guaranteed.
  </p>

  <!-- 9 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">9. Minors</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    The App is not intended for children under 13. If such data is detected, 
    contact us for removal.
  </p>

  <!-- 10 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p class="mb-6">
    We may update this Policy occasionally. Significant changes will be communicated 
    through the App or appropriate channels.
  </p>

  <!-- 11 -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3 text-[#1E758D]">11. Contact</h2>
  <div class="bg-neutral-100 border border-neutral-200 p-4 rounded-md mb-6">
    <strong>Studio Muxa Tech, S.L.</strong><br />
    Email: 
    <a href="mailto:dictionapp.muxatech@gmail.com" class="underline">
      dictionapp.muxatech@gmail.com
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
    © Studio Muxa Tech, S.L. — Privacy Policy for Dictionapp. Last updated: November 28, 2025.
  </p>
</div>

</Layout>